        <dc:title>On a Study of Layout Aesthetics for Business Process Models Using BPMN</dc:title>
        <dcterms:abstract>As BPMN spreads among a constantly growing user group, it is indispensable to analyze the expectations of users towards the appearance of a BPMN model. The user groups are mostly inhomogeneous since users stem from different backgrounds, e.g. IT, managerial sciences...</dcterms:abstract>
